<br>
Animation - if you can keep the animation alive it is great (buff, root, dot, slow, send in pet, nuke if you have to).<br>
<br>
Charm - very fun and good exp when you learn how to do when charm breaks (the key is sow/jboots and root!).<br>
<br>
Mez/nuke - use level 4 mezz and nuke if you can kill the mob before mana runs out. Very fast kills and quite safe but you need a little room to run a bit before mezz refreshes after nuking. Just tried it with animation after change of pet rules but with limited success.<br>
<br>
Then you can combine these techniques in absurdum depending what mob you face.<br>
