<br>
DC puts a whole different complexion it - now soloing is fun.  Pity we dont have a snare spell - that would make it a dream.<br>
<br>
Find your pet - Senior Guard in Kael, Sissar Reverant / Stalker in the Grey or whatever - buff it up with umbra, VoG, str then find a target &amp; pull with Tepid Deeds.  let the pet get agro &amp; add a cripple, plus any other assorted spells you may wish.<br>
<br>
My favourite is to give myself Boon of the Garou &amp; VoG &amp; join in the melee.  This gives me 232 dex on top of 255 int/cha so my SoSS can proc away nicely doing more damage for less agro than nuking would.<br>
<br>
Just remeber to keep Rune handy incase things turn nasty!<br>
